children.value: Meet Leonard the lion! Have you ever met a lion who didn't eat meat? Meet Leonard, he's a vegetarian! He loves lentils, lasagna, and learning how to code. Leonard loves naps like his older brother Richard and is helping create their website – the lion brothers!

<ProjectCard title="Richie-kun" link="https://www.behance.net/gallery/58937147/Freiheit" bg="linear-gradient(to right, #D4145A 0%, #FBB03B 100%)">
Richard spends his days napping and his nights working as a security guard. His favorite color is orange and even though helooks tough, this lion is a big softy.
</ProjectCard>
